  "text": "This is a dumb question, but… There was a movie called Battle Beyond the Stars. I don't know if you are familiar with it or not. I guess you are. It seemed to have what you're telling us included in the script. Is this correct? Do you know anything about it? I am Ra. This particular creation of your entities had some distortions of the Law of One and its scenario upon your physical plane. This is correct. I am Ra. I leave this instrument now. I leave each of you in the love and the light of the One Infinite Creator. Go forth, therefore, rejoicing in the power and the peace of the One Creator. Adonai.",
